      {
        "parameters": {
          "description": "Generate 8-12 strategic questions to clarify and validate a business idea. Questions are organized by category: problem clarification, solution refinement, hypothesis validation, and business model exploration. Use when you need to identify key unknowns or help the user refine their idea.",
